313
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:30,500
- I think I got it.
- No way.

314
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:33,200
- I think it's in there.
- Well, then look.

315
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:36,500
You look.

316
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:39,800
All right. We'll both look together.

317
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:42,800
One, two...

318
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:44,800
- Three!
- Agh!

319
00:24:45,500 --> 00:24:47,300
You idiot!

320
00:24:47,300 --> 00:24:51,000
You can't catch a bat with a pot, moron.

321
00:24:50,900 --> 00:24:53,800
You take a mop and a broom... Oh!

322
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:57,800
- Oh, God! Oh! Oh! Oh, God!
- (screeches)

323
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:07,200
Get this thing off me!
What the hell are you...

