- Please! You're aggravating it!

329
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:25,900
Why are you kicking me? Ow!

330
00:25:25,900 --> 00:25:28,400
- I can't see a damn thing!
- Die!

331
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:30,900
- Oh, Jesus!
- I think I nailed it!

332
00:25:30,900 --> 00:25:33,800
- (screeching)
- I don't believe it. He's still alive.

333
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:36,700
Can we please try my idea?

334
00:25:36,700 --> 00:25:41,800
Come on! Hold the thing tight
so it gets in there.

